T1  - A Composite Heterogeneous Model for Brand Choice Behavior
AU  - Jones, J. Morgan
Y1  - 1973/01/01
PY  - 1973
DA  - 1973/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.19.5.499
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.19.5.499
