TY  - JOUR
T1  - Note—Derivation from Queueing Theory of an Identity Related to Abel's Generalization of the Binomial Theorem, which is Useful in Graph Theory
AU  - Cooper, Robert B.
Y1  - 1973/01/01
PY  - 1973
DA  - 1973/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.19.5.582
